                            <comment id="17826827" author="ecomar" created="Wed, 13 Mar 2024 18:46:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;KafkaServer (ZKMode) needs to wait on the future returned by SocketServer.enableRequestProcessing&lt;/p&gt;

